54struct DEVCFGLOCK1_BITS { // bits description
55 Uint16 CPUSEL0:1; // 0 Lock bit for CPUSEL0 register
56 Uint16 CPUSEL1:1; // 1 Lock bit for CPUSEL1 register
57 Uint16 CPUSEL2:1; // 2 Lock bit for CPUSEL2 register
58 Uint16 CPUSEL3:1; // 3 Lock bit for CPUSEL3 register
59 Uint16 CPUSEL4:1; // 4 Lock bit for CPUSEL4 register
60 Uint16 CPUSEL5:1; // 5 Lock bit for CPUSEL5 register
61 Uint16 CPUSEL6:1; // 6 Lock bit for CPUSEL6 register
62 Uint16 CPUSEL7:1; // 7 Lock bit for CPUSEL7 register
63 Uint16 CPUSEL8:1; // 8 Lock bit for CPUSEL8 register
64 Uint16 CPUSEL9:1; // 9 Lock bit for CPUSEL9 register
65 Uint16 CPUSEL10:1; // 10 Lock bit for CPUSEL10 register
66 Uint16 CPUSEL11:1; // 11 Lock bit for CPUSEL11 register
67 Uint16 CPUSEL12:1; // 12 Lock bit for CPUSEL12 register
68 Uint16 CPUSEL13:1; // 13 Lock bit for CPUSEL13 register
69 Uint16 CPUSEL14:1; // 14 Lock bit for CPUSEL14 register
70 Uint16 rsvd1:1; // 15 Reserved
71 Uint16 rsvd2:16; // 31:16 Reserved
72};

79struct PARTIDL_BITS { // bits description
80 Uint16 rsvd1:3; // 2:0 Reserved
81 Uint16 rsvd2:2; // 4:3 Reserved
82 Uint16 rsvd3:1; // 5 Reserved
83 Uint16 QUAL:2; // 7:6 Qualification Status
84 Uint16 PIN_COUNT:3; // 10:8 Device Pin Count
85 Uint16 rsvd4:1; // 11 Reserved
86 Uint16 rsvd5:1; // 12 Reserved
87 Uint16 INSTASPIN:2; // 14:13 Motorware feature set
88 Uint16 rsvd6:1; // 15 Reserved
89 Uint16 FLASH_SIZE:8; // 23:16 Flash size in KB
90 Uint16 rsvd7:4; // 27:24 Reserved
91 Uint16 PARTID_FORMAT_REVISION:4; // 31:28 Revision of the PARTID format
92};
